"All *.amazonaws.com APIs; classified by action name (Delete*/Terminate* = destructive, Get*/List*/Describe* = read)." = "所有 *.amazonaws.com API；按操作名称分类（Delete*/Terminate* = 破坏性，Get*/List*/Describe* = 读取）。";
