/* Supply Chain panel — intro */
"Bromure scans every package fetch (npm, PyPI, Cargo, RubyGems, Maven, NuGet, Go modules, Packagist) through the host MITM and applies these policies before the agent sees the response. The in-VM `.npmrc` / `pip.conf` can only further restrict these settings — they cannot loosen them. Use the per-package allowlists for surgical overrides." = "Bromure 通过主机端 MITM 扫描每一次软件包拉取（npm、PyPI、Cargo、RubyGems、Maven、NuGet、Go modules、Packagist），并在代理看到响应之前应用这些策略。VM 内的 `.npmrc` / `pip.conf` 只能进一步收紧这些设置，永远无法放宽。如需局部例外，请使用按包配置的白名单。";

/* Supply Chain panel — age gate */
"Age gate" = "发布时间过滤";
"Refuse packages younger than the cutoff" = "拒绝比阈值更新的软件包";
"Minimum age:" = "最小发布时长：";
"%d days" = "%d 天";
"Floating refs (`latest`, semver ranges) silently resolve to the newest version older than the cutoff. Pinned references to too-fresh versions get a 451 with a clear Bromure error." = "浮动引用（`latest`、semver 范围）会被静默解析为早于阈值的最新版本。若固定引用到过新版本，将收到带有 Bromure 明确错误信息的 451 响应。";
"Exempt packages (format: `npm:axios` or just `axios`)" = "豁免软件包（格式：`npm:axios` 或直接 `axios`）";

/* Supply Chain panel — OSV */
"OSV vulnerability check" = "OSV 漏洞检查";
"Look up packages on api.osv.dev (free, no key required)" = "在 api.osv.dev 上查询软件包（免费，无需密钥）";
"Block at severity:" = "拦截严重级别：";
"Aggregates GitHub Advisory Database + PyPI advisories + Go's database + RubySec etc. Off by default — a low-severity CVE in a transitive subpackage shouldn't interrupt a workflow." = "聚合 GitHub Advisory Database、PyPI advisories、Go 数据库、RubySec 等。默认关闭——传递依赖里一个低危 CVE 不该打断工作流。";

/* Supply Chain panel — socket.dev */
"API key:" = "API 密钥：";
"The key is stored host-side only — Bromure never exports it into the VM. Calls go directly to api.socket.dev from the host's MITM proxy." = "密钥只保存在主机端——Bromure 永远不会将其导出到 VM。请求直接从主机 MITM 代理发往 api.socket.dev。";
"Block compromised packages (rogue install scripts, malware-flagged, typosquats, suspicious telemetry)" = "拦截被入侵的软件包（恶意安装脚本、被标记为恶意软件、域名抢注、可疑遥测）";
"Block packages with known CVEs" = "拦截存在已知 CVE 的软件包";
"CVE block threshold:" = "CVE 拦截阈值：";

/* Supply Chain panel — install scripts */
"Install scripts" = "安装脚本";
"Strip preinstall / install / postinstall / prepare from npm tarballs on the fly" = "动态从 npm 压缩包中剥离 preinstall / install / postinstall / prepare";
"Bromure rewrites the tarball, removes the script keys from `package.json`, and updates the registry metadata hash so npm's verification still passes for unpinned installs. Some packages (binding compilers — better-sqlite3, node-canvas, …) legitimately need install scripts; add them to the allowlist below." = "Bromure 会重写压缩包，从 `package.json` 中移除脚本字段，并更新注册表元数据哈希，因此未锁定的安装仍能通过 npm 的校验。某些软件包（绑定编译器——better-sqlite3、node-canvas 等）确实需要安装脚本；请将它们加入下方的白名单。";
"Allow install scripts for (format: `npm:better-sqlite3`)" = "允许执行安装脚本（格式：`npm:better-sqlite3`）";

/* Supply Chain panel — lockfile */
"Lockfile-pinned installs" = "由 lockfile 锁定的安装";
"Prompt before passing lockfile-pinned tarballs through unmodified (`npm ci`, `pip --require-hashes`)" = "原样放行由 lockfile 锁定的压缩包前先询问（`npm ci`、`pip --require-hashes`）";
"These installs use cryptographic integrity hashes baked into a lockfile — Bromure can't rewrite them without breaking verification. When this is on, the first lockfile-pinned fetch in a batch pops a host dialog (Allow once / 15 min / for the session / Don't allow); the entire batch follows the decision." = "这类安装依赖锁定文件中预先固化的加密完整性哈希——Bromure 无法在不破坏校验的情况下重写它们。启用此选项时，一批锁定拉取中的第一个会弹出主机端对话框（允许一次 / 15 分钟 / 整段会话 / 不允许）；整批拉取将沿用该决定。";

/* Supply Chain consent prompt — npm ci bypass */
"npm ci (lockfile-pinned install)" = "npm ci（由 lockfile 锁定的安装）";
"An agent is running `npm ci` — package tarballs come pre-pinned with cryptographic integrity hashes, so Bromure can't strip install scripts or age-filter them without breaking npm's verification.\n\nPass these tarballs through unmodified?" = "代理正在运行 `npm ci`——这些压缩包已被锁定文件附上加密完整性哈希，因此 Bromure 无法在不破坏 npm 校验的情况下剥离安装脚本或按发布时长过滤。\n\n原样放行这些压缩包吗？";

