"The hostname the agent connects to — no https:// or path. Both the credential swap and Guardrails scope to this host, so self-hosted instances work." = "代理连接的主机名——不含 https:// 或路径。凭据替换和 Guardrails 都以该主机为范围，因此自托管实例可正常工作。";
"Your real secret. Stays on macOS — the VM only ever sees a fake stand-in." = "你的真实密钥。仅保留在 macOS 上——虚拟机只会看到一个伪造的替身。";
"Variable(s) the fake secret is exported under in the VM — comma-separated for more than one. Reference these from your code / connection string." = "在虚拟机中导出伪造密钥所用的变量——多个时用逗号分隔。请在代码/连接字符串中引用它们。";
"Add credentials for any API that Bromure doesn't handle automatically (Anthropic, OpenAI, GitHub, GitLab, DigitalOcean and Kubernetes already are). The agent inside the VM only ever sees a fake token (`brm_…`); when a request leaves the VM, Bromure swaps the fake back to your real key on the way out — so your real secret never enters the sandbox." = "为任何 Bromure 不会自动处理的 API 添加凭据（Anthropic、OpenAI、GitHub、GitLab、DigitalOcean 和 Kubernetes 已自动处理）。虚拟机内的代理只会看到伪造令牌（`brm_…`）；当请求离开虚拟机时，Bromure 会在出口处把伪造令牌换回你的真实密钥——因此你的真实密钥永远不会进入沙盒。";

