"New worktree" = "新建工作树";
"Creates a git worktree branched from this tab's current commit and opens a nested agent in it." = "从此标签页当前的提交分支出一个 git 工作树，并在其中打开一个嵌套代理。";
"Task name (e.g. Website refactoring)" = "任务名称（例如：网站重构）";
"Initial prompt (optional)" = "初始提示词（可选）";
"Runs the merge in a new tab in the destination's checkout. Only committed work on this branch is merged. If it conflicts, the coding agent is started right there to resolve it automatically. The worktree isn't discarded — use “Discard worktree” once you're happy." = "在目标检出的新标签页中执行合并。只有此分支上已提交的工作会被合并。如果发生冲突，编码代理会就地启动并自动解决。工作树不会被丢弃——满意后请使用“丢弃工作树”。";
"This tab's working directory isn't available yet" = "此标签页的工作目录尚不可用";
"The workspace is likely running an older in-VM agent. Restart the workspace (Shutdown, then Start) so it picks up worktree support, then try again." = "工作区可能正在运行较旧的 VM 内代理。请重新启动工作区（先关机，再启动）以获得工作树支持，然后重试。";
"Worktree action failed" = "工作树操作失败";

